      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="20070111">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59575014/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u59575014-4.jpg" alt="鹿灵" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20070111/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20070111/" class="">第156页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59575014/" class=" " title="鹿灵">鹿灵</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="20070111">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">观人察质，必先察其平淡，而后求其聪明。＂刘卲</span>
                  &nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/20070111/">(<span class="">1回应</span>)</a>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2012-08-01 21:05</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                观人察质，必先察其平淡，而后求其聪明。＂刘卲
